<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/145.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 Edg/145.0.0.0" version="29.6.0">
  <diagram name="Page-1" id="kCU27HZkcpHPEkcK2Dm-">
    <mxGraphModel grid="1" page="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml FastDrop_ERD\n\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\n&#39; LAYOUT ENGINE + SPACING\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\n!pragma layout smetana\ntop to bottom direction\n\nskinparam backgroundColor #f8fafc\nskinparam defaultTextAlignment center\nskinparam padding 6\nskinparam nodesep 460\nskinparam ranksep 80\nskinparam ArrowColor #475569\nskinparam ArrowThickness 1.5\nskinparam componentStyle rectangle\n\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\n&#39; COLORS\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\nskinparam rectangle {\n  BackgroundColor&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;  #1e40af\n  BorderColor&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;      #1e3a8a\n  BorderThickness&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;  2\n  FontColor&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;        #ffffff\n  FontStyle&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;        bold\n  FontSize&lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;         17\n\n  BackgroundColor&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;     #bbf7d0\n  BorderColor&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;         #15803d\n  BorderThickness&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;     2\n  FontColor&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;           #15803d\n  FontStyle&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;           bold\n  FontSize&lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;            12\n\n  BackgroundColor&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;    #fef9c3\n  BorderColor&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;        #ca8a04\n  BorderThickness&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;    1\n  FontColor&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;          #000000\n  FontSize&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;           10\n  RoundCorner&lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;        60\n\n  BackgroundColor&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;      #fef9c3\n  BorderColor&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;          #dc2626\n  BorderThickness&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;      2\n  FontColor&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;            #000000\n  FontStyle&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;            bold\n  FontSize&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;             10\n  RoundCorner&lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;          60\n\n  BackgroundColor&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt; #f3e8ff\n  BorderColor&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;     #9333ea\n  BorderThickness&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt; 1\n  FontColor&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;       #6b21a8\n  FontSize&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;        10\n  RoundCorner&lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;     60\n}\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 1 — Access Control: ROLE ← EMP             ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;  ROLE  \&quot;    as ROLE      &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;role_id 🔑\&quot;  as ROLE_id   &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;role_name\&quot;   as ROLE_name &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nROLE -down- ROLE_id\nROLE -down- ROLE_name\n\nrectangle \&quot;EMPLOYEE\&quot;       as EMP       &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;employee_id 🔑\&quot; as EMP_id    &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;           as EMP_name  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;email\&quot;          as EMP_email &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;password\&quot;       as EMP_pass  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nEMP -up- EMP_id\nEMP -left- EMP_name\nEMP -down- EMP_email\nEMP -down- EMP_pass\n\nrectangle \&quot;has\&quot; as R_has &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nEMP \&quot;M\&quot; -right- R_has\nR_has \&quot;1\&quot; -right- ROLE\n\n&#39; hidden link to force ROLE+EMP on same row\nROLE -[hidden]right- EMP\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 2 — DRIVER (center hub)                    ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;DRIVER\&quot;              as DRV        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;driver_id 🔑\&quot;        as DRV_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;                as DRV_name   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;phone\&quot;               as DRV_phone  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;license_number\&quot;      as DRV_lic    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;license_expiry_date\&quot; as DRV_licexp &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;vehicle_type\&quot;        as DRV_vtype  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;status\&quot;              as DRV_status &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;is_active\&quot;           as DRV_active &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;telegram_chat_id\&quot;    as DRV_tg     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;performance_score ◎\&quot; as DRV_score  &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nDRV -up- DRV_id\nDRV -left- DRV_name\nDRV -left- DRV_phone\nDRV -left- DRV_lic\nDRV -left- DRV_licexp\nDRV -right- DRV_vtype\nDRV -right- DRV_status\nDRV -right- DRV_active\nDRV -right- DRV_tg\nDRV -down- DRV_score\n\nrectangle \&quot;can be\&quot; as R_canbe &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nEMP \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_canbe\nR_canbe \&quot;1\&quot; -down- DRV\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 2 — VEHICLE (right of DRIVER)              ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;VEHICLE\&quot;             as VEH       &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;vehicle_id 🔑\&quot;       as VEH_id    &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;model\&quot;               as VEH_model &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;capacity_kg\&quot;         as VEH_cap   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;license_plate\&quot;       as VEH_plate &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;license_expiry_date\&quot; as VEH_exp   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nVEH -up- VEH_id\nVEH -right- VEH_model\nVEH -right- VEH_cap\nVEH -right- VEH_plate\nVEH -right- VEH_exp\n\nrectangle \&quot;drives\&quot; as R_drives &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nDRV \&quot;1\&quot; -right- R_drives\nR_drives \&quot;M\&quot; -right- VEH\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 2 — ZONE (left of DRIVER)                  ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;ZONE\&quot;              as ZONE        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;zone_id 🔑\&quot;        as ZONE_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name_ar\&quot;           as ZONE_ar     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name_en\&quot;           as ZONE_en     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;city\&quot;              as ZONE_city   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;center_lat\&quot;        as ZONE_lat    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;center_lng\&quot;        as ZONE_lng    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;base_delivery_fee\&quot; as ZONE_fee    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;is_active\&quot;         as ZONE_active &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nZONE -up- ZONE_id\nZONE -left- ZONE_ar\nZONE -left- ZONE_en\nZONE -left- ZONE_city\nZONE -left- ZONE_lat\nZONE -left- ZONE_lng\nZONE -left- ZONE_fee\nZONE -down- ZONE_active\n\nrectangle \&quot;assigned_to\&quot; as R_assigned &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nDRV \&quot;M\&quot; -left- R_assigned\nR_assigned \&quot;1\&quot; -left- ZONE\n\n&#39; hidden: keep VEH — DRV — ZONE on same row\nVEH -[hidden]right- DRV\nDRV -[hidden]left- ZONE\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 3 — CUSTOMER   ORDER                       ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;CUSTOMER\&quot;           as CUST       &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;customer_id 🔑\&quot;     as CUST_id    &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;               as CUST_name  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;phone\&quot;              as CUST_phone &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;email\&quot;              as CUST_email &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;telegram_chat_id\&quot;   as CUST_tg    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;preferred_language\&quot; as CUST_lang  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nCUST -up- CUST_id\nCUST -left- CUST_name\nCUST -left- CUST_phone\nCUST -left- CUST_email\nCUST -left- CUST_tg\nCUST -left- CUST_lang\n\nrectangle \&quot;ORDER\&quot;            as ORD        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;order_id 🔑\&quot;      as ORD_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;pickup_address\&quot;   as ORD_pick   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;delivery_address\&quot; as ORD_deliv  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;weight_kg\&quot;        as ORD_wt     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;cod_amount\&quot;       as ORD_cod    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;status\&quot;           as ORD_status &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;scheduled_date\&quot;   as ORD_sched  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;is_return\&quot;        as ORD_isret  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;notes_ar\&quot;         as ORD_notes  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;delivery_fee ◎\&quot;   as ORD_fee    &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;eta ◎\&quot;            as ORD_eta    &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nORD -up- ORD_id\nORD -left- ORD_pick\nORD -left- ORD_deliv\nORD -left- ORD_wt\nORD -left- ORD_cod\nORD -right- ORD_status\nORD -right- ORD_sched\nORD -right- ORD_isret\nORD -right- ORD_notes\nORD -down- ORD_fee\nORD -down- ORD_eta\n\nrectangle \&quot;places\&quot; as R_places &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;covers\&quot;  as R_covers &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nCUST \&quot;1\&quot; -right- R_places\nR_places \&quot;M\&quot; -right- ORD\nZONE \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_covers\nR_covers \&quot;M\&quot; -down- ORD\n\nCUST -[hidden]right- ORD\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 4 — SHIPMENT                               ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;SHIPMENT\&quot;            as SHIP        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;shipment_id 🔑\&quot;      as SHIP_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;status\&quot;              as SHIP_status &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;planned_start\&quot;       as SHIP_start  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;actual_start\&quot;        as SHIP_astart &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;eta ◎\&quot;               as SHIP_eta    &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;total_distance_km ◎\&quot; as SHIP_dist   &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;total_weight_kg ◎\&quot;   as SHIP_wt     &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nSHIP -up- SHIP_id\nSHIP -left- SHIP_status\nSHIP -left- SHIP_start\nSHIP -left- SHIP_astart\nSHIP -right- SHIP_eta\nSHIP -right- SHIP_dist\nSHIP -right- SHIP_wt\n\nrectangle \&quot;delivers\&quot; as R_delivers &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;contains\&quot; as R_contains &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nDRV \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_delivers\nR_delivers \&quot;M\&quot; -down- SHIP\nSHIP \&quot;1\&quot; -right- R_contains\nR_contains \&quot;M\&quot; -right- ORD\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 5 — ROUTE_STOP   DELIVERY_ATTEMPT          ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;ROUTE_STOP\&quot;          as RS         &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;stop_id 🔑\&quot;          as RS_id      &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;sequence_number\&quot;     as RS_seq     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;address\&quot;             as RS_addr    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lat\&quot;                 as RS_lat     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lng\&quot;                 as RS_lng     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;stop_status\&quot;         as RS_status  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;actual_arrival\&quot;      as RS_arr     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;estimated_arrival ◎\&quot; as RS_eta     &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nRS -up- RS_id\nRS -left- RS_seq\nRS -left- RS_addr\nRS -left- RS_lat\nRS -left- RS_lng\nRS -right- RS_status\nRS -right- RS_arr\nRS -right- RS_eta\n\nrectangle \&quot;has_stops\&quot; as R_hasstops &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;stop_for\&quot;  as R_stopfor  &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nSHIP \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_hasstops\nR_hasstops \&quot;M\&quot; -down- RS\nORD \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_stopfor\nR_stopfor \&quot;M\&quot; -down- RS\n\nrectangle \&quot;DELIVERY_ATTEMPT\&quot; as DA         &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;attempt_id 🔑\&quot;    as DA_id      &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;attempt_number\&quot;   as DA_num     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;status\&quot;           as DA_status  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;otp_code\&quot;         as DA_otp     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;otp_verified\&quot;     as DA_otpv    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;photo_url\&quot;        as DA_photo   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;failure_reason\&quot;   as DA_reason  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nDA -up- DA_id\nDA -left- DA_num\nDA -left- DA_status\nDA -left- DA_otp\nDA -right- DA_otpv\nDA -right- DA_photo\nDA -right- DA_reason\n\nrectangle \&quot;has_attempts\&quot; as R_attempts &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;executes\&quot;     as R_executes &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nORD \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_attempts\nR_attempts \&quot;M\&quot; -down- DA\nDRV \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_executes\nR_executes \&quot;M\&quot; -down- DA\n\nRS -[hidden]right- DA\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 6 — LOCATION_PING   PERFORMANCE_SCORE      ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;LOCATION_PING\&quot;   as LP      &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;ping_id 🔑\&quot;      as LP_id   &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lat\&quot;             as LP_lat  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lng\&quot;             as LP_lng  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;accuracy_meters\&quot; as LP_acc  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;pinged_at\&quot;       as LP_at   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nLP -up- LP_id\nLP -left- LP_lat\nLP -left- LP_lng\nLP -right- LP_acc\nLP -right- LP_at\n\nrectangle \&quot;pings\&quot; as R_pings &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nDRV \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_pings\nR_pings \&quot;M\&quot; -down- LP\n\nrectangle \&quot;PERFORMANCE_SCORE\&quot;    as PS         &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;score_id 🔑\&quot;          as PS_id      &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;score_date\&quot;           as PS_date    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;deliveries_completed\&quot; as PS_compl   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;deliveries_failed\&quot;    as PS_fail    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;on_time_rate\&quot;         as PS_otr     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;avg_rating\&quot;           as PS_rat     &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;complaints\&quot;           as PS_comp    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;weighted_score ◎\&quot;     as PS_wscore  &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nPS -up- PS_id\nPS -left- PS_date\nPS -left- PS_compl\nPS -left- PS_fail\nPS -right- PS_otr\nPS -right- PS_rat\nPS -right- PS_comp\nPS -down- PS_wscore\n\nrectangle \&quot;scored_by\&quot; as R_scored &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nDRV \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_scored\nR_scored \&quot;M\&quot; -down- PS\n\nLP -[hidden]right- PS\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 7 — SHOP   PRODUCT   WAREHOUSE             ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;SHOP\&quot;           as SHOP       &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;merchant_id 🔑\&quot; as SHOP_id    &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;           as SHOP_name  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;email\&quot;          as SHOP_email &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;password\&quot;       as SHOP_pass  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nSHOP -up- SHOP_id\nSHOP -left- SHOP_name\nSHOP -left- SHOP_email\nSHOP -left- SHOP_pass\n\nrectangle \&quot;PRODUCT\&quot;        as PROD        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;product_id 🔑\&quot;  as PROD_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;           as PROD_name   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;description\&quot;    as PROD_desc   &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;price\&quot;          as PROD_price  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;stock_quantity\&quot; as PROD_stock  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;SKU\&quot;            as PROD_sku    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nPROD -up- PROD_id\nPROD -right- PROD_name\nPROD -right- PROD_desc\nPROD -right- PROD_price\nPROD -right- PROD_stock\nPROD -right- PROD_sku\n\nrectangle \&quot;makes\&quot;    as R_makes   &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;place_an\&quot; as R_shopord &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nSHOP \&quot;1\&quot; -right- R_makes\nR_makes \&quot;M\&quot; -right- PROD\nSHOP \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_shopord\nR_shopord \&quot;M\&quot; -down- ORD\n\nrectangle \&quot;WAREHOUSE\&quot;       as WH      &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;warehouse_id 🔑\&quot; as WH_id   &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;name\&quot;            as WH_name &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;location\&quot;        as WH_loc  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lat\&quot;             as WH_lat  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;lng\&quot;             as WH_lng  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\n\nWH -up- WH_id\nWH -right- WH_name\nWH -right- WH_loc\nWH -right- WH_lat\nWH -right- WH_lng\n\nrectangle \&quot;stores\&quot;               as R_stores  &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;will be shipped from\&quot; as R_shipped &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nWH \&quot;1\&quot; -left- R_stores\nR_stores \&quot;M\&quot; -left- PROD\nSHIP \&quot;M\&quot; -down- R_shipped\nR_shipped \&quot;1\&quot; -down- WH\n\nSHOP -[hidden]right- PROD\nPROD -[hidden]right- WH\n\n&#39; ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\n&#39; ║  ROW 8 — INVOICE                                ║\n&#39; ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n\nrectangle \&quot;INVOICE\&quot;        as INV        &lt;&lt;entity&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;invoice_id 🔑\&quot;  as INV_id     &lt;&lt;pk&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;payment_status\&quot; as INV_status &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;period_start\&quot;   as INV_start  &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;period_end\&quot;     as INV_end    &lt;&lt;attr&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;amount_due ◎\&quot;   as INV_due    &lt;&lt;derived&gt;&gt;\n\nINV -up- INV_id\nINV -left- INV_status\nINV -left- INV_start\nINV -right- INV_end\nINV -down- INV_due\n\nrectangle \&quot;billed_via\&quot; as R_billed   &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\nrectangle \&quot;generate\&quot;   as R_generate &lt;&lt;rel&gt;&gt;\n\nSHOP \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_billed\nR_billed \&quot;M\&quot; -down- INV\nSHIP \&quot;1\&quot; -down- R_generate\nR_generate \&quot;M\&quot; -down- INV\n\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\n&#39; LEGEND\n&#39; ══════════════════════════════════════\nlegend bottom right\n  |= Shape |= Meaning |\n  |&lt;back:#1e40af&gt;&lt;color:#ffffff&gt;  Rectangle (blue)  &lt;/color&gt;&lt;/back&gt;| Entity |\n  |&lt;back:#fef9c3&gt;&lt;color:#000000&gt;  Ellipse (gold border)  &lt;/color&gt;&lt;/back&gt;| Attribute |\n  |&lt;back:#fef9c3&gt;&lt;color:#dc2626&gt;  Ellipse (red border, bold)  &lt;/color&gt;&lt;/back&gt;| Primary Key |\n  |&lt;back:#f3e8ff&gt;&lt;color:#6b21a8&gt;  Ellipse (purple dashed) ◎  &lt;/color&gt;&lt;/back&gt;| Derived Attribute |\n  |&lt;back:#bbf7d0&gt;&lt;color:#15803d&gt;  Rectangle (green)  &lt;/color&gt;&lt;/back&gt;| Relationship |\nendlegend\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="iFXbwUAJMZKywK_-eLhv-1">
